You have nowhere near that many stars - you need to find a way to
disconnect at least half of the equipment here, but it\'s already
Christmas! You only have time to disconnect \emph{three wires}.

Fortunately, someone left a wiring diagram (your puzzle input) that
shows \emph{how the components are connected}. For example:

\if{html}{\out{<div class="sourceCode">}}\preformatted{jqt: rhn xhk nvd
rsh: frs pzl lsr
xhk: hfx
cmg: qnr nvd lhk bvb
rhn: xhk bvb hfx
